	to initialize the base class.
	* oln/core/2d/dpoint2d.hh (oln::set_super_type< dpoint2d_<C> >):
	Re-enable it.
	(oln::dpoint2d_): Use stc_get_supers to set the base class.
	(oln::dpoint2d_::super_t): Use stc_get_super to define it.

