	these macros...
	* oln/core/abstract/macros.hh: ...here, and replace the previous
	ones.
	Rename file as...
	* oln/core/macros.hh: ...this.
	Adjust header guards.
	* oln/core/abstract/internal/image_impl.hh: Adjust users.
